### About
I'm a software developer, apple fanboy and early adopter from Germany. I like podcasts, coffee, music and driving.

### Contact
You can find me on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/alexvetter), on [Tumblr](http://alexvetter.de), on [Xing](https://www.xing.com/Alexander_Vetter5), [Stack Overflow](https://stackoverflow.com/users/104779/alexvetter) and of course on [GitHub](https://github.com/alexvetter)!
